{
  "meta": {
    "id": "playback-lease-busy",
    "description": "Live playback CAPACITY-REJECTION path: every tuner busy. Identical to playback-live up to the intent, but GET /sessions/{id} returns state=FAILED, reason=R_LEASE_BUSY (no playbackUrl). useLiveSessionController.waitForSessionReady (~L421-425) detects FAILED + LEASE_BUSY and throws player.leaseBusy -> the player shows the 'all tuners in use' surface, hls.js is never reached (so this scenario needs no HLS fixture). The error surfaces at the session poll, NOT at POST /intents, so stream.start is unchanged from the happy path and the exact-path matcher's start/stop limitation does not apply here."
  },
  "capabilities": {
    "contracts.playbackInfoDecision": "absent"
  },
  "endpoints": [
    {
      "method": "GET",
      "path": "/api/v3/system/capabilities",
      "response": { "status": 200, "body": { "contracts.playbackInfoDecision": "absent" } }
    },
    {
